OL,3,C'I blame the Post Office for my
OL,4,Chusband's death': Widow speaks out
OL,6,F"There were two officers. And I think
OL,7,Fthe police also came. And I asked
OL,8,Fthem, 'where is he? Where is my
OL,9,Fhusband?' And they said he is under
OL,10,Faudit. Under investigation."
OL,12,FJayakanthan ran a string of
OL,13,Fconvenience stores. And he'd recently
OL,14,Ftaken on a branch in west London.
OL,15,FSuddenly, there was money missing from
OL,16,Fits accounts.
OL,18,F"He panicked, that's the best word. He
OL,19,Fgot scared," says Gowri.
