OL,3,C'I blame the Post Office for my
OL,4,Chusband's death': Widow speaks out
OL,6,FShe is speaking publicly for the first
OL,7,Ftime of the moment she discovered her
OL,8,Fhusband's body, in the attic of their
OL,9,Fhome.
OL,11,F"Finally we thought to kick the door
OL,12,F(down) and we went in and he was dead.
OL,13,FFor three days I didn't sleep. For
OL,14,Fthree days I was crying."
OL,16,FJayakanthan took his own life, but his
OL,17,Fwidow believes others bear some
OL,18,Fresponsibility.
OL,20,F"I think the Post Office is to blame,"
OL,21,Fshe says.
