OL,3,C'I blame the Post Office for my
OL,4,Chusband's death': Widow speaks out
OL,6,FGowri describes her husband as an
OL,7,Fambitious businessman and a generous
OL,8,Ffather, who worked hard to support
OL,9,Ftheir two young children.
OL,11,F'They said he is under audit. Under
OL,12,Finvestigation,' Gowri told ITV News
OL,14,F"It was a really bad dream for me. I
OL,15,Fwas in shock. Unexpected."
OL,17,FSlowly, Gowri rebuilt her family's
OL,18,Flife. She moved back to Sri Lanka for
OL,19,Fa while, where she had met her husband
OL,20,Fwhen they were both young children.
