OL,3,C'I blame the Post Office for my
OL,4,Chusband's death': Widow speaks out
OL,6,FShe returned to the UK, and settled in
OL,7,FLiverpool, where we met at the Royal
OL,8,FAlbert Docks.
OL,10,FBut it was only when the problems with
OL,11,Fthe Post Office's Horizon IT system
OL,12,Fbecame public knowledge that she tried
OL,13,Fto seek redress.
OL,15,FStill, her claim for compensation took
OL,16,Fthree years to settle, and it ended
OL,17,Fwith its rejection.
