OL,11,FThe Post Office panel admitted it had
OL,12,F"no reason to doubt that the audit and
OL,13,Fwhat it uncovered had a profound
OL,14,Fimpact on Mr Jayakanthan and resulted
OL,15,Fin him sadly taking his own life".
OL,17,FYet It concluded: "The discrepancies
OL,18,Fidentified during the audit cannot on
OL,19,Fthe balance of probabilities be
OL,20,Fpresumed to be Horizon shortfalls."
