OL,3,C'I blame the Post Office for my
OL,4,Chusband's death': Widow speaks out
OL,6,FKevan Jones is a Labour MP who sits on
OL,7,Fthe Post Office's Horizon
OL,8,FCompensations Advisory Board.
OL,10,F"This case is an absolutely tragic
OL,11,Fone, but one of too many
OL,12,Funfortunately," he told ITV News.
OL,14,F"The Post Office have either destroyed
OL,15,Frecords or in some cases just lost
OL,16,Fthem. Then, we should err on the side
OL,17,Fof the victim and that's what
OL,18,Fcertainly should happen in this case."
