OL,3,C'I blame the Post Office for my
OL,4,Chusband's death': Widow speaks out
OL,6,FJayakanthan's death is the fifth known
OL,7,Fsuicide associated with the Post
OL,8,FOffice scandal.
OL,10,FHe denied himself the chance to clear
OL,11,Fhis name. Gowri fights on in his
OL,12,Fabsence.
OL,14,F"In the report they believe it is not
OL,15,FHorizon. We are asking them to
OL,16,Fdisclose the Horizon system which was
OL,17,Fin the Putney Post Office," she says.
OL,19,F"It's cost me a lot. Personal.
OL,20,FFinancial. I'm a widow. And I can't
OL,21,Fchange that."
